column330: If I stood to lose only 5 cents by playing I would play. If the maximum I could win was only 5 cents I would not play.
i just went for whatever will give me the most money
consider the possiblities for both players. take my risk aversion into account  then make a choice
If the potential gain was more than the potential loss from the sure payoff  I would choose to bet.  Otherwise  I would just take the payout.

There were a couple. When I was player 2 and player 1's spot C was lower then I knew they wouldnt play  so I knew that i wouldnt get spot C. I then would play depending on if spot B was higher then the sure payoff. I did variations of that same thing.
I just compared the sure payoff w/ the average of the highlighted box.  I clicked on the higher one.
